short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides video solutions from NeetCode to help you with your coding problems

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
An extension to make it easier to access the video solutions of your favorite LeetCode content creator, NeetCode.

Instead of having to search through Youtube for video solutions, you can see the Neetcode solution with the click of a button.


You can check out the GitHub repo here: https://github.com/erenbudur/NeetHelp
